Oh, get the phone.

00:22:56.885 --> 00:22:58.385
Let's go clear out the old man's room.

00:22:59.955 --> 00:23:04.755
(Taxi Driver 3)

00:23:14.905 --> 00:23:16.875
(The grave of Baek Seon Ja)

00:23:25.315 --> 00:23:27.445
(The grave of Baek Seon Ja, Grandson, Cheon Gwang Jin)

00:23:28.385 --> 00:23:30.185
My grandma must be raising a fuss.

00:23:52.405 --> 00:23:53.405
Hey, it's me.

00:23:54.705 --> 00:23:55.775
I'm back in Korea.

00:23:57.215 --> 00:23:58.715
It's been a while. We should meet up.

00:24:25.145 --> 00:24:27.545
So, Mr. Park's memory was back briefly?

00:24:27.705 --> 00:24:28.775
Yes.

00:24:30.715 --> 00:24:32.845
He asked me for a favor.

00:24:34.115 --> 00:24:35.115
If by chance,

00:24:36.615 --> 00:24:38.115
you find Min Ho,

00:24:39.355 --> 00:24:40.425
I need you...

00:24:41.025 --> 00:24:42.995
to hold his funeral for me.

00:24:50.495 --> 00:24:53.205
When I finally regain my senses...

00:24:54.735 --> 00:24:56.405
and learn that my Min Ho is resting in peace...

00:24:58.035 --> 00:24:59.475
in a place with plenty of sunlight...

00:24:59.545 --> 00:25:03.215
and a good view of the sunset,

00:25:05.785 --> 00:25:06.785
then...

00:25:09.115 --> 00:25:10.655
I couldn't ask for anything more.

00:25:15.795 --> 00:25:18.125
Please promise me you'll do that.

00:25:21.095 --> 00:25:23.865
What on earth happened 15 years ago?

00:25:25.735 --> 00:25:27.505
I suppose Min Ho will tell us everything now.

00:25:30.035 --> 00:25:31.675
But there's one thing that's bothering me.

00:25:32.675 --> 00:25:35.315
- What? - When Jo Seong Uk came here,

00:25:35.815 --> 00:25:37.175
he was on the phone with someone.

00:25:38.115 --> 00:25:41.245
He didn't hang up until after he removed the body from the grave.

00:25:41.785 --> 00:25:42.785
It was as if...

00:25:43.715 --> 00:25:45.285
he were asking for permission.

00:25:46.685 --> 00:25:49.155
Someone else connected...

00:25:50.025 --> 00:25:51.125
to Park Min Ho's death?

00:25:51.525 --> 00:25:52.525
Yes.

00:25:54.325 --> 00:25:56.895
Someone who's stayed hidden from us this whole time.

00:25:58.905 --> 00:26:00.005
Another perpetrator.

00:26:14.385 --> 00:26:15.955
(No Smoking)

00:26:26.495 --> 00:26:27.495
Gwang Jin!

00:26:27.865 --> 00:26:30.595
Gosh, if it isn't the famous Coach Jo Seong Uk.

00:26:33.735 --> 00:26:36.875
Gwang Jin, it's been a while. How have you been?

00:26:37.335 --> 00:26:38.875
You haven't aged a day.

00:26:39.505 --> 00:26:40.505
Have a seat.

00:26:41.105 --> 00:26:42.515
Hang on, I've got a bite.

00:26:43.545 --> 00:26:44.545
All right!

00:27:05.765 --> 00:27:08.575
What was that? You made me lose the fish.

00:27:10.005 --> 00:27:11.005
Dong Hyeon.

00:27:11.535 --> 00:27:13.505
That's against the rules.

00:27:14.045 --> 00:27:16.915
I told you to shake it after I catch the fish, you idiot.

00:27:18.175 --> 00:27:20.885
I'm sorry, it was my fault!

00:27:21.045 --> 00:27:24.055
Please let me live just this once.

00:27:24.455 --> 00:27:26.425
- Please! - Just this once?

00:27:28.925 --> 00:27:29.925
Okay.

00:27:30.555 --> 00:27:32.325
Let's get it right this time.

00:27:33.765 --> 00:27:36.565
- Let's do it! - No!

00:27:37.165 --> 00:27:38.295
Help me!

00:27:43.805 --> 00:27:44.805
Seong Uk, come over here.

00:27:51.885 --> 00:27:53.445
Hey, what's all this about?

00:27:53.985 --> 00:27:56.954
Suddenly, our game's rules broke.

00:27:56.955 --> 00:27:58.755
Then Min Ho sent a text,

00:27:58.825 --> 00:28:02.095
and now, someone else who knows everything has appeared.

00:28:03.725 --> 00:28:06.125
Dong Hyeon's always been terrible at explaining things.

00:28:06.665 --> 00:28:08.695
I can't make heads or tails of what he's saying.

00:28:09.165 --> 00:28:10.195
Gwang Jin!

00:28:11.035 --> 00:28:12.765
The bobber's moving!

00:28:16.505 --> 00:28:17.505
Pay it no mind.

00:28:17.575 --> 00:28:19.505
No, I'm telling you, the bobber moved.

00:28:20.345 --> 00:28:23.575
- That jerk is just lying. - No...

00:28:25.515 --> 00:28:26.885
Do you want to hear a secret?

00:28:28.015 --> 00:28:29.985
- What? - There are...

00:28:30.685 --> 00:28:33.425
no fish here.

00:28:52.345 --> 00:28:54.775
Since Dong Hyeon is so bad at explaining things,

00:28:55.945 --> 00:28:59.185
why don't you explain it so I can understand?

00:29:05.225 --> 00:29:06.625
Why did you dig up Min Ho?

00:29:13.525 --> 00:29:16.565
According to the DNA results, the man missing for 15 years...

00:29:16.635 --> 00:29:17.935
was a match for Park Min Ho.

00:29:20.635 --> 00:29:22.435
And what did they determine was the cause of death?

00:29:22.905 --> 00:29:25.244
It is presumed that the death was caused by a skull fracture,

00:29:25.245 --> 00:29:27.305
but the direct cause is a traffic accident.

00:29:28.045 --> 00:29:29.215
A traffic accident?

00:29:29.475 --> 00:29:32.215
Yes. He had many compound fractures all over his body.

00:29:34.385 --> 00:29:37.255
The body will be transferred to the hospital morgue today.

00:29:37.955 --> 00:29:40.385
I'll call ahead so you can claim the body.

00:29:40.925 --> 00:29:42.725
Yes, thank you.

00:29:42.755 --> 00:29:46.125
(Violent Crimes Unit, Phishing Investigation Unit)

00:29:49.365 --> 00:29:50.935
A traffic accident?

00:30:21.765 --> 00:30:22.735
I took it.

00:30:25.835 --> 00:30:28.165
All right.

00:30:34.045 --> 00:30:36.315
Min Ho, it's been a while.

00:30:36.375 --> 00:30:37.575
(Body Bag, Name: Park Min Ho)

00:30:37.875 --> 00:30:38.885
Take it.

00:30:43.485 --> 00:30:47.885
(Rainbow Taxi)

00:30:47.925 --> 00:30:48.955
Chief Park.

00:30:51.425 --> 00:30:55.435
(The Late Park Min Ho)

00:30:57.035 --> 00:30:58.035
Excuse me.

00:30:59.165 --> 00:31:01.365
There's been an accident.

00:31:02.235 --> 00:31:03.235
An accident?

00:31:03.805 --> 00:31:05.175
What are you talking about?

00:31:05.845 --> 00:31:07.545
What do you mean Park Min Ho's body was stolen?

00:31:08.345 --> 00:31:10.515
We were waiting for the body too.

00:31:10.775 --> 00:31:13.045
Apparently, they staged an accident and only took the body.

00:31:15.245 --> 00:31:17.255
But who on earth would do something like that?

00:31:22.425 --> 00:31:24.695
- Everyone. - What is it, Go Eun?

