Isn't it rude to invite someone over and then just call him?

00:40:43.455 --> 00:40:44.585
Look to your right.

00:40:48.525 --> 00:40:51.295
See that door with the X on it? Come in through there.

00:41:08.045 --> 00:41:09.045
So?

