A survival game.

00:43:12.035 --> 00:43:14.935
If you win, Min Ho's bones are yours.

00:43:16.175 --> 00:43:17.305
If I win,

00:43:18.275 --> 00:43:19.905
I'll just throw them away.

00:43:51.405 --> 00:43:54.175
All right.

00:43:54.675 --> 00:43:55.805
Start!

00:44:01.145 --> 00:44:02.815
Round One.

00:44:03.585 --> 00:44:04.585
Fight.

